    <stitle>International&#174; T 444E Diesel Engine Service, Model Year 1994 - 1998 - CRANKCASE, CRANKSHAFT, CONNECTING
        RODS AND PISTONS - Flywheel and Housing - Check Crankshaft Pilot Concentricity
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Check Crankshaft Pilot Concentricity</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Attach a dial indicator magnetic base to the flywheel housing and place the indicator tip
                against the flywheel pilot.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Rotate the crankshaft slowly and record the total indicator variation. Refer to the
                specification for concentricity tolerance.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
